# KMRTM40045-SPI 4.0" TFT Display (480x320 v2.1)

## Summary

Successfully initialized and drove the KMRTM40045-SPI 4.0" TFT display using an ESP32 and TFT_eSPI.

Display responds correctly with full-screen color rendering and text output.

---

## ⚠️ Critical Discovery

The display is labeled:

**KMRTM40045-SPI (ST7796 expected)**

However:

❌ ST7796 driver does NOT work
✅ ILI9488 driver works perfectly

---

## ✅ Working Driver Configuration

```cpp
#define ILI9488_DRIVER
```

---

## 🔌 Working Pin Configuration

```cpp
#define TFT_MOSI 23
#define TFT_SCLK 18
#define TFT_CS    5
#define TFT_DC    2
#define TFT_RST   4

#define TFT_BL 15
#define TFT_BACKLIGHT_ON HIGH
```

---

## 🔧 Wiring

| Display Pin | ESP32 Pin |
| ----------- | --------- |
| VCC         | 3.3V      |
| GND         | GND       |
| CS          | GPIO 5    |
| RESET       | GPIO 4    |
| D/C         | GPIO 2    |
| SDI (MOSI)  | GPIO 23   |
| SCK         | GPIO 18   |
| LED         | GPIO 15   |

