## ❌ Non-Working Configuration

```cpp
#define ST7796_DRIVER
```

Result:

* White screen
* Flickering only
* No visible graphics

---

## 🧠 Observations

* Display likely uses an ILI9488-compatible controller despite ST7796 labeling
* Mislabeling or controller substitution is common in generic TFT modules
* Always validate hardware through testing, not documentation alone

